Welcome to a Ultimate Surrender's Tag Team league match up.
Team Orange vs Team Purple. Four girls,
non-scripted, real tag team action.

The rules are set: (1) Three tags per team, per round.
(2) Three 12-minute non-scripted wrestling rounds. (3)
Last round consists of the winners tying up,
dominating, humiliating, and brutally fucking the
losers. IN FRONT OF A LIVE AUDIENCE!

Team Orange: Is looking for their first win, and it has to be today! Another loss and they will be out of the play off picture. This is a must win for Orange and they know it!

Team Purple: Is back to full strength. Alexa has returned from her injury. With a record of (1-1) Purple must also win the match up to have a shot at making the playoffs. No other color performs better as a team then purple!

Both teams knew what was at stake. Both teams put everything they had on the mat. After multiple lead changes, and 36 minutes of wrestling the match was decided in the very last second by only 1 point! This is the most exciting Tag Team match to date! Join, and be amazed.
